{"tid":1898184,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺依一萬蚊係不義之財","createTime":"2020-02-26T04:09:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T23:35:32.000Z","uid":139294,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e2859a368a0e4296a7772098dda4d80d08061f42","tid":1898184,"uid":139294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T04:09:54.000Z","msg":"回望番過去8個月發生既事<br />\n依一萬蚊其實係政府用嚟維穩<br />\n拉走淺黃 令藍屍繼續跪低幫政府含<br />\n覺唔覺依啲錢係沾滿鮮血而得嚟<br />\n我想大家係拎到錢既同時<br />\n可唔可以唔好掛住吃喝玩樂玩<br />\n諗下點用依筆錢 去幫下其他人<br />\n至少 捐一千蚊都好掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75fba38eca6d6433a657e88f17b0975c0f8e0edb","tid":1898184,"uid":139294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T04:10:56.000Z","msg":"錢照收 政府繼續反！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48babca0e5010eba276cc8f30ace13e3094e9442","tid":1898184,"uid":258598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T04:16:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb94e422d898e197b410fa24041caf5be1be9cf5","tid":1898184,"uid":139294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T04:16:37.000Z","msg":"自私閪仆街死"},{"pid":"160f5f84e3c61910150765d1eae4e79173e2d0f7","tid":1898184,"uid":139294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"48babca0e5010eba276cc8f30ace13e3094e9442","tid":1898184,"uid":258598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T04:16:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T04:18:50.000Z","msg":"放心.我會 <br />\n我捐左你跟機ok?"},{"pid":"09965d424fe89bbcdf8ebe2de05f0d2d18791cd8","tid":1898184,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"160f5f84e3c61910150765d1eae4e79173e2d0f7","tid":1898184,"uid":139294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"48babca0e5010eba276cc8f30ace13e3094e9442","tid":1898184,"uid":258598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T04:16:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-0